{"tid":1481942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政治問題 政治解決 將所有責任指向政權","createTime":"2019-08-18T02:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T00:46:18.000Z","uid":113373,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9a2d847d9a21eff1b7197a51744497fe1978b4","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我哋要警察同香港人都覺得，香港政府先係罪魁禍首，全因政府唔聽民意，強推送中條例，唔會應香港人訴求，利用警察作為擋箭牌<br />\n<br />\n再盲目針對警察其實真係冇意思，<span style=\"color: red;\">武力抗爭應該有目標咁去做</span>，而唔係每次都搵警察嚟做，每次都要武力抗爭會唔會成為我哋最反感嘅「教條主義」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續亂用武力針對警察，論武力，我哋唔會贏，論機會，恐怕前線拉曬都未成功</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">梁天琦 28/7/2019<br />\n<br />\n當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。<span style=\"color: red;\">但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span><br />\n<br />\n我時常提醒自己：<span style=\"color: red;\">政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。</span><br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，<span style=\"color: red;\">我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？</span></span>"},{"pid":"01998464ba2e6ce0eb67d5f9b11874481fd9c267","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望更多人明白</span>"},{"pid":"063c6331d6e03d3bd1ee33ffa29d7647507788eb","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>希望大家唔好行錯方向<br />\n<br />\n對準政權 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span>"},{"pid":"82fe81b62f914f7ede9f6a9f7e1c6de3f6d29e09","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:26:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一陣維園見</span>"},{"pid":"3d8de3af4de09f6c7469652d46014999ec1d0a75","tid":1481942,"uid":251051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed71e589d09a20dbc0197228082ef98421e7a90b","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:47:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a1418b09e9cf7640b475cc237eb7ce11e6b8ed5","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"703166104669635bd4887119d10dafa65cf05763","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n2pm見 <br />\n大家唔好遲到呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a96f0b78a16e0794ea268ab433a445a3150678","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"149bef9dc0d2f852550186e64e5100dcc3ab3437","tid":1481942,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57b802cca96d84bcc582720ad117f09b2dce20ed","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"69 616 71 818"},{"pid":"8ce5910f6289834909dd6795887b19a981f90af9","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"265da858de9e83a893e9365f2e055cdfe34a71fc","tid":1481942,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RYzfG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RYzfG8.jpg&h=87ccabfb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEyvytP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEyvytP.jpg&h=58e1d00a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"895354